relevant_communication:
In the scope of its mission, the LU EMN NCP has the following tasks: 

1) answers ad-hoc queries launched by the other EMN NCP's and the European Commission.  
2) Drafts four thematic studies per year in accordance with the Work Programme established by the Steering Board of the EMN;  
3) organises thematic conferences on migration and asylum;  
4) coordinate the EMN Platform on Statelessness established as a result of the JHA Council conclusions of 4 December 2015; 
5) provides up to date information to national and european stakeholder on migration and asylum from the Luxembourg perspective
